                      <div class="uui-text-size-medium">Most air fresheners are mostly water, alcohol and propellant. Scent Bomb is 100% pure concentrated fragrance oil — a single bottle goes far, and the scent lasts all day, often into the next.</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="uui-layout18_item">
                    <div class="uui-layout18_item-icon-wrapper">
                      <div class="uui-icon-featured-outline-large">
