              <div class="max-width-80ch">
                <div class="heading-component">
                  <div class="max-width-80ch">
                    <div class="heading-4">9 Scent Bomb Fragrances Available in Canada</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="max-width-45ch">
                    <div>From sweet Black Cherry to crisp Hawaiian Blue — 9 concentrated fragrances in a 1 oz bottle that lasts for weeks. One spray, instant transformation.</div>
