  <!-- HOW TO USE -->
  <section class="htu-section">
    <div class="htu-wrap">
      <div class="htu-head">
        <div class="htu-eyebrow"><span class="htu-dot"></span>How to use</div>
        <h2 class="htu-heading">How to use Scent Bomb air freshener for best results</h2>
        <p class="htu-sub">Scent Bomb is simple to use, but a few small things make a big difference. Follow these five steps and one bottle will last a long time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="htu-steps">
        <div class="htu-step">
          <div class="htu-num">1</div>
          <div class="htu-step-content">
            <h3 class="htu-step-title">Hold the bottle 1–2 inches from the surface.</h3>
            <p class="htu-step-desc">Get close. You’re applying oil to a specific spot, not misting a room.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="htu-step">
          <div class="htu-num">2</div>
          <div class="htu-step-content">
            <h3 class="htu-step-title">Spray onto a surface — never into the air.</h3>
            <p class="htu-step-desc">Because it’s pure oil, spraying it into the air leaves a film that makes hard floors slippery. Aim at a floor mat, under a seat, or inside a bin instead.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="htu-step">
          <div class="htu-num">3</div>
          <div class="htu-step-content">
            <h3 class="htu-step-title">Start with 1–2 sprays.</h3>
            <p class="htu-step-desc">That’s genuinely enough for a car interior or a small bathroom. You can always add more — you can’t take it back.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="htu-step">
          <div class="htu-num">4</div>
          <div class="htu-step-content">
            <h3 class="htu-step-title">For larger rooms, spray once or twice in each corner.</h3>
            <p class="htu-step-desc">This spreads the scent evenly instead of concentrating it in one spot. Works for the whole house with just one bottle.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="htu-step">
          <div class="htu-num">5</div>
          <div class="htu-step-content">
            <h3 class="htu-step-title">Use the cotton-ball trick.</h3>
            <p class="htu-step-desc">Spray onto a cotton ball and tuck it wherever you want a discreet, steady scent — a closet, a drawer, behind a toilet, under a car seat. Releases fragrance for days.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="htu-step htu-step-desktop-only">
          <div class="htu-num">6</div>
          <div class="htu-step-content">
            <h3 class="htu-step-title">Take it everywhere you go.</h3>
            <p class="htu-step-desc">The 1 oz bottle is small enough to slip into your pocket, purse, glove box or carry-on. Keep one in your bag and another in your car — a five-second odor fix is always within reach, wherever life takes you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="htu-cta-wrap">
        <a href={AMAZON_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="htu-cta">Shop on Amazon →</a>
        <p class="htu-cta-note">Made in the USA · Shipped from Canada · 9 fragrances</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

