                <div class="max-width-40ch">
                  <div class="heading-6">Bathroom &amp; Toilet — the ultimate pre-poop toilet spray and bathroom air freshener. The 3-drop trick: spray 3 times directly into the bowl water before use. The concentrated oil creates a barrier that traps poop odors before they rise — works as a pre-poop spray, bathroom deodorant spray, or air freshener for any room.</div>
